# ToDoList Application

A simple and efficient task management application built with **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript** to help you organize and track your daily tasks.

---

## 📋 Overview

This ToDoList app allows users to:
- ✅ Add new tasks
- ✏️ Edit existing tasks
- 🗑️ Delete completed or unwanted tasks
- 📝 Mark tasks as complete/incomplete
- 💾 Persist data using browser storage
- 🎯 Organize tasks efficiently

---

## 🚀 Features

### Core Functionality
- **Add Tasks**: Quickly add new items to your to-do list
- **Mark Complete**: Toggle task completion status
- **Edit Tasks**: Modify task descriptions
- **Delete Tasks**: Remove tasks you no longer need
- **Local Storage**: Tasks persist even after closing the browser

### User Interface
- Clean, intuitive design
- Responsive layout
- Easy-to-use controls
- Visual feedback for task status

---

